heduling, Dijkstra's algorithm"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Since you're a full-stack engineer working on Gen AI, heaps are essential for efficient beam search in LLM generation (keeping top-K tokens), top-K token sampling for probability-based selection, and priority-based task scheduling in distributed AI systems."}]}]}}
